  <entry>
    <title>Linux 下安装JDK 和 TOMCAT</title>
    <link href="http://yywsy.github.io/2018/04/30/Linux%20%E4%B8%8B%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85JDK%20%E5%92%8C%20TOMCAT/"/>
    <id>http://yywsy.github.io/2018/04/30/Linux 下安装JDK 和 TOMCAT/</id>
    <published>2018-04-30T15:43:50.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-05-02T16:21:40.026Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="1准备安装包"><a href="#1准备安装包" class="headerlink" title="1准备安装包"></a>1准备安装包</h3><p><em>万恶的Oracle 没办法用wget 下载jdk了，只有yum的openJDK还能下,但是这货是OpenJDK。。。只能自备安装包</em></p><p>  JDK:  jdk-8u45-linux-x64.tar.gz <a href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">下载链接</a><br>  TOMCAT:  apache-tomcat-7.0.86.tar.gz<a href="https://tomcat.apache.org/download-70.cgi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">下载连接</a></p><h3 id="2-在、usr-local-下建文件夹java，tomcat7-0"><a href="#2-在、usr-local-下建文件夹java，tomcat7-0" class="headerlink" title="2.在、usr/local/下建文件夹java，tomcat7.0"></a>2.在、usr/local/下建文件夹java，tomcat7.0</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# cd /usr/local</span><br><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# mkdir java </span><br><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# mkdir tomcat7.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-把压缩包分别放进服务器对应文件夹去"><a href="#3-把压缩包分别放进服务器对应文件夹去" class="headerlink" title="3.把压缩包分别放进服务器对应文件夹去"></a>3.把压缩包分别放进服务器对应文件夹去</h3><pre><code>用ssh工具直接拖拽上传更方便</code></pre><h3 id="4-解压jdk，tomcat"><a href="#4-解压jdk，tomcat" class="headerlink" title="4.解压jdk，tomcat"></a>4.解压jdk，tomcat</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# tar -vxzf jdk-8u45-linux-x64.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# tar -vxzf apache-tomcat-7.0.86.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-配置Java环境变量（Tomcat可以不配直接用）"><a href="#5-配置Java环境变量（Tomcat可以不配直接用）" class="headerlink" title="5.配置Java环境变量（Tomcat可以不配直接用）"></a>5.配置Java环境变量（Tomcat可以不配直接用）</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]#  vim /etc/profile #使用vim打开配置文件（也可以直接下载到本地修改再传回服务器，替换原文件）</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line">   #在文件结尾追加环境变量 （vim 使用 i 键进入编辑模式，esc键退出编辑，进入常规模式，dd快速删除一行，：wq保存退出，：q!强制退出不保存）</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line">   JAVA_HOME=/usr/local/java/jdk1.8.0_45</span><br><span class="line">   PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$PATH</span><br><span class="line">   CLASSPATH=.:$JAVA_HOME/lib/dt.jar:$JAVA_HOME/lib/tool.jar</span><br><span class="line">   export JAVA_HOME</span><br><span class="line">   export PATH</span><br><span class="line">   export CLASSPATH</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line">   #这里其实和windows的环境变量差不多，只不过，path用：分割</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>保存并退出编辑器，这时候可以选择重启或者使用命令使改动生效。<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# source /etc/profile</span><br><span class="line"># [root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# . /etc/profile </span><br><span class="line"># 注意：这里 . 与 / 之间存在一个空格 </span><br><span class="line">#若在当前目录在/etc/，那么可以直接执行./profile，这里 . 与 /没有空格</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="6-验证Java"><a href="#6-验证Java" class="headerlink" title="6.验证Java"></a>6.验证Java</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# java -version</span><br><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# javac -version</span><br><span class="line">#正确显示版本号即成功，也可以用vim写个helloWorld来测试一下</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><ul><li><p>过程中遇到的坑：</p><p>  -有的CentOS自带openJDK,要先卸载。</p>  <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# getconf LONG_BIT  #查看当前操作系统位数</span><br><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# java -version  #查看Java版本</span><br><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# rpm -qa | grep java  #列出Java安装路径</span><br><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# rpm -e –-nodeps java-1.6.0-openjdk-1.6.0.0-1.45.1.11.1.el6.x86_64</span><br><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# rpm -e –-nodeps java-1.6.0-openjdk-headless-1.6.0.0-1.45.1.11.1.el6.x86_64</span><br><span class="line">#noarch结尾的文件不用卸</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  -验证的时候提示权限不够，要重新分配一下。<br><em>-bash: /usr/local/java/jdk1.8.0_45/bin/java: Permission denied</em></p>  <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat ~]# su root  #获取root用户权限</span><br><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat java]# chmod 770 jdk1.7.0_80/bin/java</span><br><span class="line">[root@VM_0_15_redhat java]# chmod 770 jdk1.7.0_80/bin/javac</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  -PATH写错了，被追加很多次，需要改<a href="">参照此篇</a></p></li></ul>]]></content>
    
